SUMMARY:Fox Creek Whiffle-Dodger Day (Swannanoa)
DESCRIPTION:Join the Friends of Fox Creek Park and Swannanoa Valley WILD for a workday and celebration at Fox Creek Park. As we all emerge from the cold of winter\, it’s finally time to celebrate the return of spring! We’ll be planting native wildflowers\, clearing trails\, and cleaning up the park. There will be free food and music to enjoy. All are welcome! Please park at the Swannanoa Library and stroll down to the park at 111 Ivanhoe Drive.
URL:https://ncwf.org/event/fox-creek-whiffle-dodger-day-swannanoa/
CATEGORIES:Featured
END:VEVENT
